title: 99. Becoming Unstoppable Ft. Tia-Clair Toomey
itunes:title: 99. Becoming Unstoppable Ft. Tia-Clair Toomey
description: Why stop at great when you can become unstoppable? On today's episode, Andy and Sal are joined by Commonwealth Games Gold Medalist and CrossFit Athlete, Tia-Clair Toomey as they discuss what it takes to be a world champion, how to use negativity as fuel and how we are all capable of anything in life as long as we're willing to put in the work.
